General Electric Co. (GE)  appointed
Canan Ozsoy as chief executive and country chairwoman of its
operations in  Turkey , the company said.  Ozsoy, who replaced Kursat Ozkan, was the general manager
of GEâ€™s General Mammography operations before the appointment,
the Fairfield, Connecticut-based company said in an e-mailed
statement late yesterday.  Ozsoy, who will command a workforce of more than 600 in
Turkey, is a graduate of the University of Istanbul Department
of Dentistry and has an MBA from Bosphorus University of
